description: Howard Quayle says he will continue to "work from home" after testing positive for Covid-19.
title: Coronavirus: Isle of Man Chief Minister Howard Quayle tests positive
title_page: Coronavirus: Isle of Man Chief Minister Howard Quayle tests positive - BBC News
maintext: After displaying some symptoms earlier this week, Mr Quayle had a Covid-19 test on Tuesday, the results of which have now been confirmed as positive.
